    "headline": "Deckers’s (NYSE:DECK) Q1 CY2026 Sales Beat Estimates, Stock Soars",
    "summary": "Footwear and apparel conglomerate Deckers (NYSE:DECK) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2026, with sales up 9.6% year on year to $1.12 billion. The company’s full-year revenue guidance of $5.89 billion at the midpoint came in 1.1% above analysts’ estimates. Its GAAP profit of $0.96 per share was 15.6% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
