    "summary": "GOLETA, Calif., May 21, 2026--Deckers Brands (NYSE: DECK), a global leader in designing, marketing, and distributing innovative footwear, apparel, and accessories, today announced financial results for the fourth fiscal quarter and full fiscal year ended March 31, 2026. The Company also provided its financial outlook for the full fiscal year ending March 31, 2027 and a multi-year financial framework for the fiscal years ending March 31, 2028 through March 31, 2030.",
